dct_title_s: Great Britain and Ireland : with ye judges circuits
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. "To face Vol. I, p. CXLVIII." Inset maps: Shetland Islands -- [Western Isles]. Includes triangular table showing distances between cities and shire towns. Map shows boundaries, rivers and settlements. Ferro meridian. From: New British atlas : being a complete set of county maps, on which are delineated all the roads, cities, towns, villages, rivers & canals; together with correct general maps of England, Wales, Scotland & Ireland / [engraved by J. Cary]. London : Printed for John Stockdale ..., 1805.
